        "new_rules_in_this_unit": [
            "Combine verbs with the accusative prepositions für or gegen to express what one is for/against: demonstrieren für/gegen, sich interessieren für, sich entscheiden für/gegen, kämpfen für/gegen + accusative.",
            "Use denn (coordinating conjunction, position zero, verb stays second) or da (subordinating conjunction, verb to end) as alternatives to weil for expressing reasons."
        ],
